# =============================================================
# Trivy Ignore File
# =============================================================
# Add CVE IDs here to suppress known vulnerabilities that have
# been reviewed and accepted as non-applicable or mitigated.
# Format: One CVE ID per line
# Docs: https://aquasecurity.github.io/trivy/latest/docs/configuration/filtering/
# =============================================================

# Example (uncomment to use):
# CVE-2023-XXXXX
# CVE-2024-XXXXX
